===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈwɔ:təʃɛd/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A region of land within water flows down into a specified body, such as a river, lake, sea, or ocean; a [[drainage basin]] or [[catchment basin]].
# The [[topographical]] [[boundary]] dividing two adjacent [[catchment basin]]s.
# The time after which material of more adult nature ([[violence]], [[swear word]]s, [[sex]]) can be [[broadcast]] in the [[media]].
# A [[critical]] [[point]] marking a change in course or development.

